        arch_philosophy_h: "Design Philosophy: Security-First",
        arch_philosophy_p: "PassForge follows Zero Trust + Local Zero Knowledge principles. The master password is NEVER accessible on disk, in logs, in recoverable memory, or even by the application developer. This model ensures that only the user, at the moment of authentication, possesses the decryption capability.",
        arch_layers_h: "Multi-Layered Key Derivation",
