        sec_design_philosophy_h: "1. Design Philosophy (Security-First)",
        sec_design_philosophy_p: "Goal: The Master Password must NEVER be accessible on disk, in logs, in recoverable memory, or even by the developer. This model adopts the Zero Trust + Local Zero Knowledge approach.",
